<div class="row full-band">
  <div class="columns small-6 ">
    <div class="home-panel panel-text" style="vertical-align:middle">
      <h2>Interactive content for today's attention span.</h2> 
      <p>Use Tiles to connect with employees in a way that's relevant for them. Tiles are bite-sized, visual and fun so employees read, understand and participate.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="columns small-6">
      <div class="home-panel" style1="">

      <%=image_tag("landing/tilevsemail.png")%>
    </div>
  </div>
 
</div>

<div class="row  full-band">

  <div class="columns small-6">
    <div class="home-panel" style="background-image:url(<%=image_path('landing/organize-inf.gif')%>)">
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="columns small-6">
    <div class="home-panel panel-text" style="padding-top:15%">
      <h2>One place to get many priorities done.</h2> 
      <p>
      Post Tiles about company news, benefits, events and more to your organization’s Board, a private site hosted by Airbo. Whereas an intranet is like a filing cabinet that stores content out of view, Airbo is like a bulletin board that showcases what's new.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="row 6 full-band">
  <div class="columns small-6 ">
    <div class="home-panel panel-text" style="padding-top:15%" >
      <h2>Track engagement in real-time.</h2> 
      <p>
      See that employees read content, spend less time following up, and find out what employees are interested in.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="columns small-6">
      <div class="home-panel" style="background-image:url(<%=image_path("landing/measure-inf.gif")%>)">
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row">

  <div class="small-10 columns small-centered center-panel">
    <div class="row">
      <h2 class="text-center padded-v-20">Easy to Use.</h2>
      <div class="small-4 columns center-panel">
        <%=image_tag "landing/sb-wellness-icon01.png"%>
        <h3>1. Add Tiles to Your Board</h3>
        <p> Copy Tiles from a robust library, or create your own in minutes.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="small-4 columns center-panel">
        <%=image_tag "landing/sb-wellness-icon02.png"%>
        <h3>2. Engage Employees</h3>
        <p>New Tiles are summarized in an attention-grabbing email that you send to employees every 1 to 2 weeks.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="small-4 columns center-panel" >
        <%=image_tag "landing/sb-wellness-icon03.png"%>
        <h3>3. See Results</h3>
        <p>Employees use the email to log into Airbo. As they interact with Tiles, you see real-time activity and feedback.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>


<div class="row full-band">
  <div class="columns small-6 ">
    <div class="home-panel" >
      <h2>Explore Tiles</h2> 
      <p>
      See how other companies are using Airbo to engage their employees. Get Ideas. Copy what you like.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="columns small-6">
  </div>
</div>


